# --- Option A (default): same-origin proxy ---
# Leave NEXT_PUBLIC unset: the app calls `/vtoa-api`, and Next.js rewrites to FastAPI
# (see `next.config.ts`). Set backend origin for the rewrite (server-only):
# VTOA_BACKEND_ORIGIN=http://127.0.0.1:8000

# --- Option B: call FastAPI directly from the browser ---
# Local:
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8000
# Production (Vercel):
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=https://vtoa-api.onrender.com

# When using Option A, set the FastAPI server's PUBLIC_BASE_URL to your Next origin + /vtoa-api
# so `output_image_url` is same-origin (see vota-be/.env.example).
